{"id":"2faf29ed4460cdb1adda970b8f09c14a6712df14bf334d3dcd3fb12dece75e30","item_id":"e3e6177180:0","text":"此 pattern 会将输入置换值变换到自定义数值范围，用作 PxrDisplace 的输入。这包括重映射置换中心，并将其变换到不同的置换尺度和空间。"}
{"id":"154a7d9fcbcc650f614354163ee73beeda98b5fdc8e5cb196fe924fe697371b2","item_id":"e3e6177180:1","text":"需要将此 pattern 的结果连接到"}
{"id":"650fd33d487fcce791c04e96b9683b3a3edd28bf0817fcb504a18f6c54ceffa7","item_id":"e3e6177180:2","text":"PxrDisplace"}
{"id":"dbd0e024c247c11de99f578b8a98d1fc1a3bd60db7695315663c969bbb659ed6","item_id":"e3e6177180:3","text":"的 Scalar 或 Vector Displacement 输入，才能置换几何体。"}
{"id":"a4dc940c4cc858929c91d805f7bc162d02325c52194f4f80bc78b67d5483bd9d","item_id":"e3e6177180:5","text":"Displacement Type"}
{"id":"c5b49288292a5f1ffcd50deedd636690fac4094b4e0b8a16c82caf9dbbd61a82","item_id":"e3e6177180:6","text":"指定输入的 Displacement Type（置换类型）。"}
{"id":"7e8ab303c062230808b28e88256761e7eb5d6e5cab47efcb6c487133f85c3270","item_id":"e3e6177180:7","text":"1: Scalar."}
{"id":"e5776253b03c858a997a1fec79e9e1e569299d030be946fd166227ac18142088","item_id":"e3e6177180:8","text":"这是浮点类型。"}
{"id":"75f2810be1f84a01b9cf367daa74fd4a9adcae88d343bc6e5193e1ac312c8522","item_id":"e3e6177180:9","text":"2: Generic Vector."}
{"id":"a38d51ddd02701d1a58b4862b93d387753af229b28c4d85482f5865d51b11e0f","item_id":"e3e6177180:10","text":"这可以是任意程序化创建或贴图生成的向量，不需要像 Mudbox 或 ZBrush 矢量置换贴图那样进行特殊解码。"}
{"id":"984d754299c874cf4fe18efb45422a0d24d4680c88e69d1fe82aa6b9d0760990","item_id":"e3e6177180:11","text":"3: Mudbox Vector."}
{"id":"7d29eb28179300a529e351651b5d25115b476b0e82cd279830e411c04cde4d2e","item_id":"e3e6177180:12","text":"这是从 Mudbox 提取的矢量置换贴图。"}
{"id":"283dc9a6b685795cda6cf67e34d87a26c85027477b5a34fd32b9208b57cb276e","item_id":"e3e6177180:13","text":"4: ZBrush Vector."}
{"id":"544ab41e52c8c0a7843e0d5f79b5f2c2aec37a5a611cd241b7420213df6b4016","item_id":"e3e6177180:14","text":"这是从 ZBrush 提取的矢量置换贴图。"}
{"id":"d6f6f6a4bf1f35729549bae3f9249c5eac5a1699fded62b1403a58375955187c","item_id":"e3e6177180:16","text":"Scalar displacement（标量置换）输入。这是 float displacement（浮点置换）。连接一个"}
{"id":"1a7c808d3df8dd47920a1e81830e0360106667a7275834c38e216fb8e15db6cc","item_id":"e3e6177180:18","text":"或任意 float pattern 节点到此参数。"}
{"id":"9ed492cfc806b3dd99058530ceec9ce6fc891e88836ab7605b5fba4012a7380b","item_id":"e3e6177180:56","text":"仅当 Displacement Type 设置为 Scalar 时有效。"}
{"id":"9ed492cfc806b3dd99058530ceec9ce6fc891e88836ab7605b5fba4012a7380b","text":"仅当 Displacement Type 设置为 Scalar 时有效。"}
{"id":"f244aee0ad1d09b4094537e2b89e063a6cf593475285f362d43eaeb6845afc43","item_id":"e3e6177180:21","text":"Vector displacement 输入。Vector displacement data 是三通道 XYZ 数据。将 PxrTexture 或任意 RIS vector pattern 节点的 resultXYZ 或 resultRGB 连接到此参数。"}
{"id":"ace95ccc5b979229527cb8e8b4a7bd25f3aa0dfccca5c7494d14d511db44f9bf","item_id":"e3e6177180:22","text":"仅当 Displacement Type 为 Vector 时有效。"}
{"id":"c4da660ec1e5ee89668dfaf5111a048e914abde6551837134eccc274115159b1","item_id":"e3e6177180:23","text":"Vector Space"}
{"id":"9580e50c914591682c804480ebf39a593f2705a4d9fab66ce50193a5e1999e40","item_id":"e3e6177180:24","text":"指定向量创建时所在的空间。对于 Mudbox 和 ZBrush vector type，这会是导出矢量置换时使用的空间。"}
{"id":"33a92f322552405148dd994d97de0563ae63a2d7e86c51f65698befd25f83146","item_id":"e3e6177180:25","text":"1: World"}
{"id":"31ffddde6072a0f6bdc2f96442c8b0259c627df384bd856c97e48026d46e1856","item_id":"e3e6177180:26","text":"2: Object"}
{"id":"ca58fa469bbd3e0c92a1cba38c22eeb55a1e2258f01992039cc21d7e6d6442c2","item_id":"e3e6177180:27","text":"3: Tangent"}
{"id":"fa14fd8163502e7a934b936205bdc9b563b11297c2be3e97d4921333f6d6c4ab","item_id":"e3e6177180:28","text":"4: Current"}
{"id":"20d98703e6e184b9eedec39b64daccd859cd65825b2c4a6f2a31efa109f75f33","item_id":"e3e6177180:29","text":"设置正确的 Vector Space 非常重要，否则生成的矢量置换会渲染错误。"}
{"id":"8ad1a3f340e9cd481169578c571a1c95008ae447a88b2873b3ad3d11f0f5cfdd","item_id":"e3e6177180:30","text":"大多数情况下，如果出现意外结果，原因都是 Vector Space 设置不正确。"}
{"id":"8f22b9aef67192a049daa5dda7e581aebb066986b25fcda2b976c0e4a4afd94a","item_id":"e3e6177180:31","text":"对于 Mudbox，矢量置换需要从 Mudbox 以 Absolute Tangent 导出，而不是 Relative Tangent。"}
{"id":"8e9acd1a4d3eb25ac4080f61d35833ae711f3ca954c234047f84af74f291719d","item_id":"e3e6177180:32","text":"Displacement Height"}
{"id":"29579e42cf7c7d760e3d07836d14f7dd27bd7b72d651fe79d963613ecd205048","item_id":"e3e6177180:33","text":"Displacement Height 作用于向外置换的置换值。"}
{"id":"39a911afb42a69d879ec393a7213a289939c80647f1521820f2604e1f395206a","item_id":"e3e6177180:34","text":"Displacement Depth"}
{"id":"b184e0d91132afd29b576682368208f8fc86e1794e24f35ba7dd14413ea1b02c","item_id":"e3e6177180:35","text":"Displacement Depth 作用于向内置换的置换值。"}
{"id":"56229d86bb182d95841c8ad236091d2a9f5a7cfbb426c3d3ce80d2baf951f11e","item_id":"e3e6177180:36","text":"Remapping Mode"}
{"id":"820de0e4cbae63785255699cd5851804e934121cba8d33ba0f6bd8bff07fce34","item_id":"e3e6177180:37","text":"指定如何重映射置换值："}
{"id":"2a446c1d35014d13f95c557cb133c5b9eeaae143ac6e2d749f758a615dfcdb1d","item_id":"e3e6177180:38","text":"1: None."}
{"id":"9c4c68d36d147f98e66fc6e08ce95484224132981fdc223d8ebebd16f176fdac","item_id":"e3e6177180:39","text":"按原样读取置换值，不进行任何重映射。使用 Displacement Height 缩放置换值。"}
{"id":"b0260d77bfd223b21552d957b1b3c5af379a7161c0a860d8a538b4326037f1f8","item_id":"e3e6177180:40","text":"2: Centered:"}
{"id":"9220a343e7017cdeccd29d894c6f9ecbeef2460ae51521b420b6d8ab47a94d43","item_id":"e3e6177180:41","text":"置换值会以指定的 Displacement Center 为中心。如果该值等于中心，则不会产生置换。"}
{"id":"644fefe2d867766bb89748da4c22a1d28c5b54631560e0947244a9db52922972","item_id":"e3e6177180:42","text":"低于中心的任何值都会向内置换，高于中心的任何值都会向外置换。"}
{"id":"581149b9751c8bd53c883d94a8a4d57fd25a1b0f11b07b5f803de997edc3613b","item_id":"e3e6177180:43","text":"3: Interpolate Depth and Height:"}
{"id":"3c078fe43595cd9e5888b525186979f3b0af06b7a0b8fd5e002d6a0b3a007efa","item_id":"e3e6177180:44","text":"通过 catmull-rom spline（spline(\"catmullrom\", -depth, -depth, 0, height, height)）拟合指定的 Displacement Depth 和 Displacement Height。此模式不使用 Displacement Center。"}
{"id":"b797da3dfb9618c61bcc7885b707e195f9021c26cebaf108582dad308e056294","item_id":"e3e6177180:45","text":"Displacement Center"}
{"id":"733c17d1719ceff088b59bf46e0f01193e9870a327674131a2ca74a0b18b6e76","item_id":"e3e6177180:46","text":"用于 \"Centered\" Remapping Mode 的 Displacement Center。"}
{"id":"08189012aa48a4c7955be8b338d7c117910f0dbf29fe7d50aaf081f957d5ae6c","item_id":"e3e6177180:47","text":"Displacement Scale Space"}
{"id":"be8e07ac654733aae9e44d9d45cc024670324db3003ab82ce34aa3b7c1c16d6f","item_id":"e3e6177180:48","text":"用于测量置换单位的空间。例如 \"world\"、\"object\" 或用户定义的坐标系统。"}
{"id":"cedaf49cfd1abb7eea59df1bb070315b81c4688cd7baf3046d4454d2e6eedd51","item_id":"e3e6177180:49","text":"我们提供两个用于指定置换的渲染空间：world 和 object space。"}
{"id":"b041f37a44117ddddcfa2de2e3621461b3253330e0f1e504161c41f2c6356705","item_id":"e3e6177180:50","text":"默认情况下，RenderMan 会在 Object space 中置换。这通常适合雕刻模型。但对某些对象来说，这可能导致不连续。例如，一组一起置换的对象，像由一组平面组成的环境部件。在 object space 中，这些对象可能会像下方示例一样，在面片之间产生缝隙或不连续。"}
{"id":"b04f060937ed71e883fe4dfdfae799b5355358464435ee6a5cabd3885a1e2b15","item_id":"e3e6177180:51","text":"要修正这个特定场景，可以选择 World Space，用相同的八个面片获得下方结果。这会解决海面平面、悬崖和岩石等问题，在这些情况下置换会跨多个形状共享。"}
{"id":"bf0c3ecd30cc0942a8ce29208b09d1e717688b09d1f38c8e40c26a4195ae251e","item_id":"e3e6177180:52","text":"Use Displacement Direction"}
{"id":"f01ce03dd10e64844d295f549184e41ebd3dc1b70bccea85d7286d3679d4c6fe","item_id":"e3e6177180:54","text":"开启时，置换会沿下方提供的置换方向进行，而不是沿表面法线。"}
{"id":"b5add7ecbcac5432d49d7cdaec1467b8adc6fe41d1fd2d272d13c21d8fac46fc","item_id":"e3e6177180:55","text":"Displacement Direction"}
{"id":"68ad63a657543aae4b2710ee112155c7b0c215abc641f676475d22c641427ec2","item_id":"e3e6177180:57","text":"置换会沿此项所指向的方向进行，而不是沿表面法线。请注意，置换方向向量在使用前会被归一化。"}
{"id":"5e560f32e21a6dd2bc129ff7f1aa17174714303b7503e5eb6e62c19f56b8817f","item_id":"e3e6177180:58","text":"Displacement Direction Space"}
{"id":"850750e0a71cbe47374badd3ec02798813d25c6295d2a9e9c5d4c4d34de9b00a","item_id":"e3e6177180:59","text":"置换方向向量所在的空间。例如 \"world\"、\"object\" 或用户定义的坐标系统。"}
{"id":"f3c2e0cb416a2cc1652481a52b5d55975473472d6839077e80829736ac8cbefb","item_id":"e3e6177180:62","text":"矢量结果。"}
{"id": "e8756d05615a8b9aac2d138a9ae82553f3231ff237868a66679a30001b4f326b", "item_id": "e3e6177180:4", "text": "Input Parameters（输入参数）"}
{"id": "ddf9afdd443e2577dd48cedfa6b905a1cb7c215b7e3d85564f6f71a7a8484be4", "item_id": "e3e6177180:15", "text": "Scalar Displacement"}
{"id": "ccc6ebd6189c8d8f6fed82ba1bfef6ebca467a2b94a4677ddb9068b32719f8d7", "item_id": "e3e6177180:17", "text": "PxrTexture"}
{"id": "b84c3fc76a6d996fe5573a9b78d2502728998886dc853d641cc50b65d37629ab", "item_id": "e3e6177180:20", "text": "Vector Displacement"}
{"id": "8b76e2df9050f924b018cff8809cbc580f39a71664984ae54adf99defe9eaa2e", "item_id": "e3e6177180:60", "text": "Output Parameters"}
{"id": "35f6e1ebb9b040db4e992f8d8fb554d4bc9ad8ea924c6744adc8ae3f58bc3498", "item_id": "e3e6177180:61", "text": "resultXYZ"}
